# To enable sysreq key
create a file at /etc/sysctl.d/99-sysctl.conf with contents kernel.sysreq=1

# To suppress error msg on screensaver
Edit hidden file in home directory:
~/.xscreensaver

Change the option:
captureStderr: True
to
captureStderr: False
and
overlayStderr: True
to
overlayStderr: False

